Hey Miner, 



Do you believe that the price of Bitcoin correlates with positive features in the media?



We definitely sense some kind of buzz. It seems like happier times in the cryptocurrency industry are here! 

We might be overly optimistic but can you blame us after being featured on 60 Minutes? 

On May 19th, one of America’s most popular TV shows aired its first ever coverage of Bitcoin. It’s huge for Genesis Mining, and it’s great for the whole industry as well. Finally Bitcoin is getting some spotlight again! 



If you haven't seen the show, watch it

here
